    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "solar tide (tides caused by the Sun)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "潮の満ち引きは主に月の引力によるものだが、太陽潮の影響も無視できない要素だ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "月と太陽が一直線上に並ぶ新月や満月の時には、太陰潮と太陽潮が重なり合って大潮となる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "海洋学の講義で、太陽の引力が海水の昇降に与える太陽潮のメカニズムについて学んだ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      }
